data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 1,324 sqft is perfect for families. The back yard features a covered patio, pool with a safety fence around it and half of the yard is dedicated to a grassy area for pets or children to play. Recent updates include new pool equipment, a smart thermostat, alarm system, as well as new flooring. The new flooring and updated kitchen make the home feel modern and comfortable. With plenty of space for everyone, this home is perfect for families looking for a comfortable and stylish place to call home. Don't forget to take the virtual tour and schedule your showing today!
